memberdef.name: key_callback

briefdescription.para: This class lets you create actions, so you can bind inputs to actions.

detaileddescription.para: This class can be used to create/delete custom actions, to bind and configure a button, and to associate methods with this custom action so that they are called when the action is triggered by pressing the associated button.
